Package: PairMarker
Type: Package
Title: Pairwise Gene Marker Discovery for Binary Phenotypes
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("twl-00", email = "tanwenlu2000@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for pairwise gene comparison, chi-square screening,
    Fisher exact testing, and multiple-testing correction for discovering
    gene-pair markers associated with binary phenotype labels.
